  m_text: "Fever:\nA warm anti-inflammatory drink that strengthens immunity and reduces
    fever discomfort. \n                                                                                                                                             
    \nAcid Reflux: \nSoothes the digestive system and helps reduce acid-related irritation.\n\nAllergy:\nBoosts
